    "The dataset consists of 42061 training samples, 4672 dev, and 4693 test samples.",
    "Success on this task is typically measured by achieving high BLEU, NIST, METEOR, Rouge-L, and CIDEr scores, as presented in the paper.",
    "• DART: This is a large dataset for opendomain record-to-text generation published in (Nan et al., 2021).",
    "It has a total of close to 82K samples.",
    "The underlying task is rdf-totext (mapping entity relations to text)."
